"It was a really sloppy goal, we had opportunities to clear it. When they went up 1-0, they made it very difficult for us to get some fluidity in the game.
"Fair play to them, they produced three points from it. I don't think they offered much to the game going forward but defensively they stuck to the task.
"We moved the ball well, got it wide early and put some fantastic crosses in but we just weren't ruthless enough in both boxes."
